quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  54,28,Wa Nabbi'hum 'Anna Al-Mā'a Qismatun Baynahum Kullu Shirbin Muĥtađarun
  54,29,Fanādaw Şāĥibahum Fata`āţá Fa`aqara
  54,30,Fakayfa Kāna `Adhābī Wa Nudhuri
  54,31,Innā 'Arsalnā `Alayhim Şayĥatan Wāĥidatan Fakānū Kahashīmi Al-Muĥtažiri
  54,32,Wa Laqad Yassarnā Al-Qur'āna Lildhikri Fahal Min Muddakirin
  54,33,Kadhabat Qawmu Lūţin Bin-Nudhuri
  54,34,Innā 'Arsalnā `Alayhim Ĥāşibāan 'Illā 'Āla Lūţin Najjaynāhum Bisaĥarin
  54,35,Ni`matan Min `Indinā Kadhālika Najzī Man Shakara
  54,36,Wa Laqad 'Andharahum Baţshatanā Fatamāraw Bin-Nudhuri
  54,37,Wa Laqad Rāwadūhu `An Đayfihi Faţamasnā 'A`yunahum Fadhūqū `Adhābī Wa Nudhuri
  54,38,Wa Laqad Şabbaĥahum Bukratan `Adhābun Mustaqirrun
  54,39,Fadhūqū `Adhābī Wa Nudhuri
  54,40,Wa Laqad Yassarnā Al-Qur'āna Lildhikri Fahal Min Muddakirin
  54,41,Wa Laqad Jā'a 'Āla Fir`awna An-Nudhuru
  54,42,Kadhabū Bi'āyātinā Kullihā Fa'akhadhnāhum 'Akhdha `Azīzin Muqtadirin
  54,43,Akuffārukum Khayrun Min 'Ūla'ikum 'Am Lakum Barā'atun Fī Az-Zuburi
  54,44,Am Yaqūlūna Naĥnu Jamī`un Muntaşirun
  54,45,Sayuhzamu Al-Jam`u Wa Yuwallūna Ad-Dubura
  54,46,Bali As-Sā`atu Maw`iduhum Wa As-Sā`atu 'Ad/há Wa 'Amarru
  54,47,Inna Al-Mujrimīna Fī Đalālin Wa Su`urin
  54,48,Yawma Yusĥabūna Fī An-Nāri `Alá Wujūhihim Dhūqū Massa Saqara
  54,49,Innā Kulla Shay'in Khalaqnāhu Biqadarin